name: schemaName
description: The name of the schema tracked

name: objectName
description: The name of the table/object tracked

name: startTimeTZ
description: Generated helper column to hold the time zone ID for 'startTime'.

name: startTime
description: The timestamp for when the refill started.

name: endTimeTZ
description: Generated helper column to hold the time zone ID for 'endTime'.

name: endTime
description: The timestamp for when the refill ended.

name: timeInsertSec
description: The time, in seconds, the inserts took.

name: timeDeleteSec
description: The time, in seconds, the deletes took.

name: timeAnalyzeSec
description: The time, in seconds, the analyze took.

name: created
description: The timestamp for when the record was created. (TILDA.RefillPerf)

name: lastUpdated
description: The timestamp for when the record was last updated. (TILDA.RefillPerf)

name: deleted
description: The timestamp for when the record was deleted. (TILDA.RefillPerf)
